      <title>土耳其在加息前经济增速超越中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/turkish-economy-booms-in-growth-spurt-before-rate-hikes-kick-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其经济扩张速度超过中国，今年初其经济增长速度位居全球前列，这很可能是其在一系列大幅加息后进入降温阶段前的最后一次冲刺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/turkish-economy-booms-in-growth-spurt-before-rate-hikes-kick-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 07:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
